          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-surface-variant/30 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-xl p-5 cursor-pointer group">
          <summary class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface text-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            How much protection does corrugated cardboard provide?
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-4">
            Corrugated cardboard's honeycomb structure provides excellent cushioning and impact resistance. A single-wall sheet protects against minor impacts and vibration. Double-wall sheets protect against medium impacts and compression. Triple-wall sheets provide heavy-duty protection for fragile or valuable items.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-surface-variant/30 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-xl p-5 cursor-pointer group">
