      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Corrugated cardboard sheets are the unsung heroes of packaging. These versatile materials serve 10+ critical functions that extend box life, reduce damage, organize shipments, and ultimately lower total packaging costs. Whether you're protecting fragile items, building custom compartments, or padding furniture, corrugated sheets are indispensable.
      </p>
