        By understanding the various uses and choosing the right sheet type (single-wall, double-wall, or triple-wall), Malaysian businesses can optimize their packaging strategy, reduce damage rates, and maintain cost efficiency.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        Contact Quinocycle today to source bulk corrugated cardboard sheets with custom sizing, competitive pricing, and expert packaging consultation for your business.
      </p>
